## APIs Ativas

```
GET  djzeneyer/v1/menu?lang=en          → Menu de navegação
GET  djzeneyer/v1/products?lang=en      → Produtos WooCommerce
POST djzeneyer/v1/subscribe             → Newsletter
GET  djzeneyer/v1/config                → Configuração global do site

POST zeneyer-auth/v1/register           → Cadastro
POST zeneyer-auth/v1/login              → Login (email/senha)
POST zeneyer-auth/v1/google             → Google OAuth
GET  zeneyer-auth/v1/auth/validate      → Validar JWT
GET  zeneyer-auth/v1/profile            → Perfil do usuário logado

GET  zengame/v1/me                      → Dashboard do usuário (points, rank, achievements)
GET  zengame/v1/leaderboard?limit=10    → Ranking público

GET  zen-bit/v2/events                  → Lista de eventos
GET  zen-bit/v2/events/:slug            → Detalhe do evento
```

